<p>PSTMA offers a range of undergraduate and postgraduate programs in various fields of medicine, including medicine, dentistry, nursing, physical therapy, and public health. The academy is known for its rigorous and comprehensive curriculum, which is designed to provide students with a strong foundation in both theoretical and practical aspects of medicine.</p>

<h3>Facilities:</h3>

<p>The academy has state-of-the-art facilities, including well-equipped laboratories, lecture halls, and a large library with an extensive collection of medical literature. The campus is spread over several buildings and provides a comfortable and conducive learning environment for students.</p>
<h3>Faculty:</h3>

<p>PSTMA has a highly qualified faculty consisting of experienced medical professionals and researchers. The faculty is dedicated to providing students with personalized attention and support, and they encourage students to pursue their interests and passions in the field of medicine.</p>

<h3>Research and Innovation:</h3>

<p>The academy is actively involved in research and innovation, with a particular focus on developing new treatments and medical technologies. PSTMA has a number of ongoing research projects in various fields of medicine, and students are encouraged to participate in these projects and contribute to the advancement of medical knowledge.</p>

<h3>International Collaboration:</h3>
<p>PSTMA has established partnerships with several leading medical institutions and universities from around the world. These partnerships provide opportunities for students and faculty to participate in exchange programs, joint research projects, and other collaborative initiatives.</p>


